title: Mera Desh Mera Dharam
subTitle: Sajid, the son of an army officer, joins an armed freedom struggle in a bid to liberate the Bangladeshi populace from the oppressive Pakistani regime. However, his personal life faces turmoil.

title: Holi Ayee Re
subTitle: Taking advantage of her trusting nature, an unprincipled man seduces a village maiden, only to desert her in her time of need.

title: Suhana Safar
subTitle: Enticed by his poetry, Sapna travels to India from the US to meet the poet Ujjwala. There, she meets a man, Sunil, who falls for her but he decides to help her meet Ujjwala.

title: Ghar Ka Chiraag
subTitle: Kiran marries Kumar, believing her love, Ravi, to be dead. When Ravi returns years later, Kiran is forced to confront the painful secrets surrounding her past and her marriage.

title: Bhrashtachar
subTitle: Journalist Bhavani intends to expose and bring to justice a corrupt politician who pretends to be a social worker. However, she soon finds herself trapped in a web of conspiracies.

title: Raeeszada
subTitle: When Sanjay, a policeman, arrests Jagannath, a gangster, his senior disagrees and frees the goon. Sanjay decides to resign and fight corruption on his own.

title: Gaban
subTitle: Ramanath, the unemployed son of an honest clerk, gets arrested for embezzlement and faces prison time. The only way he can set himself free is to testify against freedom fighters.

title: BadKaar
subTitle: Mini, a young woman, is kidnapped from a pub and police investigate the case. However, when her sister sets out to find her, she uncovers a criminal nexus which shakes the city.

title: Andaz
subTitle: Sheetal, a widow, is a school teacher and lives with her son after her husband's death. She meets her student's father Ravi, a widower, and decides to marry him.

title: Hitler
subTitle: Siddhanth Sharma, a strict disciplinarian, is forced to chase hi brother, Amar, after he is accused of murder. However, his wife, Sheila, a lawyer, decides to defend Amar.
